{"tid":301038,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［月經］Non-BBA grad 白紙想入銀行做","createTime":"2017-06-28T10:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T07:05:10.000Z","uid":10271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"adfee64b5d25d59680184241ff38fb9ba76c71a8","tid":301038,"uid":10271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"想問下各位巴打有咩post 會考慮請non-bba 嘅白紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟 non-三大 non-bba 2:2 grad 想搵銀行工做<br />\n<br />\n唔介意人工比其他 u-grad 低，想入去學嘢同儲吓銀行方面嘅經驗<br />\n<br />\n我知依家普遍都係請 contract，想問下直接同間銀行 apply 定經 agent 會機會大啲？<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果開個價低啲會唔會彌補到無經驗同成績差嘅問題？（雖然我知應該都唔會）<br />\n<br />\n最近留意到有個entry post 請人，係 operation support officer - broking service<br />\n見佢個 salary range 係 11~15K，同埋open to various academic background<br />\n<br />\n本身想做吓啲資料搜集，但係 google 完無咩人提過，睇佢啲 requirement 同 responsibilities 都好空泛，想問下有無巴打可以分享吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感激 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c92ff5bcdbf3dce6736729645a72d8f236d248","tid":301038,"uid":49861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:07:46.000Z","msg":"一開始入做teller 點都請，人工12k , 一年考灑保險加178 ，轉Assistant 18k , 再一年轉rm 28k"},{"pid":"a9e0c1668705cf2af8c778124cea98ae75367567","tid":301038,"uid":77936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一開始入做teller 點都請，人工12k , 一年考灑保險加178 ，轉Assistant 18k , 再一年轉rm 28k</blockquote><br />\nteller14k起吓? 12k個啲真係畀hr水"},{"pid":"c05f8698d3d62a4c41c525f450a59b79494d60b5","tid":301038,"uid":10271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"係咪唔做 teller 就無第二條路？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47adea024d