:41:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪唔做 teller 就無第二條路？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nu grad 就唔好做teller啦<br />\n你本身想做front定back office?"},{"pid":"01fa3038987de507eadf0aee10c351d477a93e23","tid":301038,"uid":10271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:17:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>非商科，之前apply過clerk位都有叫我in，話係做分行operation，12k,，不過最後冇做</blockquote><br />\n點解唔做嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過咁，如果你係想係銀行界發展，唔建議做依d clerk，冇career path可言</blockquote><br />\n就係諗緊做clerk 或者teller 都儲唔到啲有助轉其他銀行工嘅經驗，想睇下有無依啲以外嘅位可以做吓"},{"pid":"5084422a0a68aacd939243c27f3694fd679bf5b9","tid":301038,"uid":10271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係咪唔做 teller 就無第二條路？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nu grad 就唔好做teller啦<br />\n你本身想做front定back office?</blockquote><br />\nBack office 係咪比較少要追數同畀人捽？<br />\n自問口才同 bba 果啲比差得遠，驚做唔黎啲要追數嘅位，不過如果有機會都會想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6b1108de368845c0692b676c162262d37ed218","tid":301038,"uid":10271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T18:23:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>非商科，之前apply過clerk位都有叫我in，話係做分行operation，12k,，不過最後冇做</blockquote><br />\n點解唔做嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有第二份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第二份係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  透唔透露得<br />\n比較之下 clerk 果份太伏？"},{"pid":"d832b1c7690997a8bced7398c7a6b4356c4e7cbd","tid":301038,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0